QuestData.Title: Warden Hamoot
QuestData.Description: Before you leave Cenarion Refuge, make sure you speak with Warden Hamoot. He's in charge of the expedition's security.$B$BHe would never forgive me if I didn't send a seasoned adventurer like you his way.
QuestData.LogDescription: Report to Warden Hamoot at the Cenarion Refuge in Zangarmarsh.
QuestData.RewardText: Ysiel sent you? Of course I can use someone like you! We're always in need of a little muscle.
